Package de.ukbonn.mwtek.dashboard.interfaces

Interface DataRetrievalService

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDataRetrievalService, AcuwaveDataRetrievalService, FhirDataRetrievalService
public interface DataRetrievalService
This interface provides all the retrieval methods needed to supply the corona dashboard with the necessary data, regardless of the server type.

    • getPatients

      List<org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Patient> getPatients(List<de.ukbonn.mwtek.utilities.fhir.resources.UkbObservation> listUkbObservations, List<de.ukbonn.mwtek.utilities.fhir.resources.UkbCondition> listUkbConditions)
      The retrieval of FHIR UkbPatient resources.
      Parameters:
      listUkbObservations - A list of all FHIR observation resources that include a covid finding.
      listUkbConditions - A list of all FHIR condition resources that include a covid diagnosis.
      Returns:
      A list of all patient resources that have at least one covid observation and/or covid diagnosis.

    • getProcedures

      List<org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Procedure> getProcedures()
      The retrieval of FHIR UkbProcedure resources.
      Returns:
      A list of all requested FHIR procedure resources that contain artificial ventilation data for patients with at least one covid observation and/or covid diagnosis.

    • getProcedures

      List<org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Procedure> getProcedures(List<de.ukbonn.mwtek.utilities.fhir.resources.UkbEncounter> listUkbEncounters, List<de.ukbonn.mwtek.utilities.fhir.resources.UkbLocation> listUkbLocations, List<de.ukbonn.mwtek.utilities.fhir.resources.UkbObservation> listUkbObservations, List<de.ukbonn.mwtek.utilities.fhir.resources.UkbCondition> listUkbConditions)
      The retrieval of FHIR UkbProcedure resources. The input resources are needed for a preprocessing filtering in the acuwave sided procedure data retrieval.
      Parameters:
      listUkbEncounters - A list of all FHIR encounter resources of the detected patients after a specified cut-off date.
      listUkbLocations - A list of all FHIR location resources that are referenced in any encounter resources.
      listUkbObservations - A list of all FHIR observation resources that include a covid finding.
      listUkbConditions - A list of all FHIR condition resources that include a covid diagnosis.
      Returns:
      A list of all requested FHIR procedure resources that contain artificial ventilation data for patients with at least one covid observation and/or covid diagnosis.
